 Hunter]]'' by [[Daniel Nettheim]]\n*''[[In Darkness (2011 film)|In Darkness]]'' by [[Agnieszka Holland]]\n*''[[Intruders (2011 film)|Intruders]]'' by [[Juan Carlos Fresnadillo]]\n*''[[Jeff Who Lives at Home]]'' by [[Jay Duplass]] and [[Mark Duplass]]\n*''[[Keyhole (film)|Keyhole]]'' by [[Guy Maddin]]\n*''[[Killer Joe (film)|Killer Joe]]'' by [[William Friedkin]]\n*''[[Life Without Principle (film)|Life Without Principle]]'' by [[Johnnie To]]\n*''[[Like Crazy (2011 film)|Like Crazy]]'' by [[Drake Doremus]]\n*''[[Low Life (2011 film)|Low Life]]'' by [[Nicolas Klotz]]\n*''[[Martha Marcy May Marlene]]'' by [[Sean Durkin]]\n*''[[Mausam (2011 film)|Mausam]]'' by [[Pankaj Kapoor]]\n*''[[Melancholia (2011 film)|Melancholia]]'' by [[Lars von Trier]]\n*''[[Monsieur Lazhar]]'' by [[Philippe Falardeau]]\n*''[[The Moth Diaries (film)|The Moth Diaries]]'' by [[Mary Harron]]\n*''[[My Worst Nightmare]]'' by [[Anne Fontaine (filmmaker)|Anne Fontaine]]\n*''[[The Oranges (film)|The Oranges]]'' by [[Julian Farino]]\n*''[[Pearl Jam Twenty]]'' by [[Cameron Crowe]]\n*''[[Rampart (film)|Rampart]]'' by [[Oren Moverman]]\n*''[[Rebellion (2011 film)|Rebellion]]'' by [[Mathieu Kassovitz]]\n*''[[Salmon Fishing in the Yemen]]'' by [[Lasse Hallstr\u00f6m]]\n*''[[Shame (2011 film)|Shame]]'' by [[Steve McQueen (director)|Steve McQueen]]\n*''[[A Simple Life]]'' by [[Ann Hui]]\n*''[[The Skin I Live In]]'' by [[Pedro Almod\u00f3var]]\n*''[[Sleeping Beauty (2011 film)|Sleeping Beauty]]'' by [[Julia Leigh]]\n*''[[Take Shelter]]'' by [[Jeff Nichols]]\n*''[[10 Years (2011 film)|10 Years]]'' by [[Jamie Linden (writer)|Jamie Linden]]\n*''[[Terraferma (film)|Terraferma]]'' by [[Emanuele Crialese]]\n*''[[A Burning Hot Summer|A Burning Hot Summer (That Summer)]]'' by [[Philippe Garrel]]\n*''[[Trishna (2011 film)|Trishna]]'' by [[Michael Winterbottom]]\n*''[[Twixt (film)|Twixt]]'' by [[Francis Ford Coppola]]\n*''[[Tyrannosaur (film)|Tyrannosaur]]'' by [[Paddy Considine]]\n*''[[Violet & Daisy]]'' by [[Geoffrey 