ise Lost 3: Purgatory]]'' by [[Joe Berlinger]] and [[Bruce Sinofsky]]\n*''[[Paul Williams Still Alive]]'' by [[Stephen Kessler]]\n*''[[Pink Ribbons, Inc.]]'' by [[L\u00e9a Pool]]\n*''[[Samsara (2011 film)|Samsara]]'' by [[Ron Fricke]]\n*''[[Sarah Palin: You Betcha!]]'' by [[Nick Broomfield]] and [[Joan Churchill]]\n*''[[The Story of Film: An Odyssey]]'' by [[Mark Cousins (film critic)|Mark Cousins]]\n*''[[Surviving Progress]]'' by [[Mathieu Roy (director)|Mathieu Roy]] and [[Harold Crooks]]\n*''[[The Tall Man (documentary)|The Tall Man]]'' by [[Tony Krawitz]]\n*''[[Undefeated (2011 film)|Undefeated]]'' by [[Daniel Lindsay]] and [[T.J. Martin]]\n*''[[Urbanized]]'' by [[Gary Hustwit]]\n*''[[Whores' Glory]]'' by [[Michael Glawogger]]\n\n===Vanguard===\n*''[[Carr\u00e9 blanc]]'' by [[Jean-Baptiste L\u00e9onetti]]\n*''[[Doppelg\u00e4nger Paul]]'' by [[Kris Elgstrand]] and [[Dylan Akio Smith]] \n*''[[Generation P (film)|Generation P]]'' by [[Victor Ginzburg (director)|Victor Ginzburg]]\n*''[[Headshot (2011 film)|Headshot]]'' by [[Pen-Ek Ratanaruang]]\n*''[[Hidden Driveway]]'' by [[Sarah Goodman]]\n*''[[i am a good person/i am a bad person]]'' by [[Ingrid Veninger]]\n*''[[Love and Bruises]]'' by [[Lou Ye]]\n*''[[Oslo, August 31st]]'' by [[Joachim Trier]]\n*''[[Snowtown (film)|Snowtown]]'' by [[Justin Kurzel (director)|Justin Kurzel]]\n*''[[The Year of the Tiger]]'' by [[Sebasti\u00e1n Lelio]]\n\n===TIFF kids===\n*''[[First Position]]'' by [[Bess Kargman]]\n*''[[The Flying Machine (film)|The Flying Machine]]'', by [[Martin Clapp]], [[Geoff Lindsey]] and [[Dorota Kobiela]]\n*''[[A Letter to Momo]]'' by [[Hiroyuki Okiura]]\n*''[[A Monster in Paris]]'' by [[Bibo Bergeron]]\n\n===Mavericks===\n*''[[Barrymore]]'' by [[Eric Canuel]]\n*''[[Deepa Mehta and Salman Rushdie]]''\n*''[[In Conversation With...Francis Ford Coppola]]''\n*''[[The Island President]]'' by [[Jon Shenk]]\n*''[[The Love We Make]]'' by [[Bradley Kaplan]] [[Albert and David Maysles|Albert Maysles]]\n*''[[Neil Youn