ave It on the Floor]]'' by [[Sheldon Larry]]\n*''[[Nuit 1]]'' by [[Anne \u00c9mond]]\n*''[[The Odds (film)|The Odds]]'' by [[Simon Davidson]]\n*''[[The Patron Saints]]'' by [[Brian M. Cassidy]] and [[Melanie Shatzky]]\n*''[[Romeo Eleven]] (Rom\u00e9o Onze)'' by [[Ivan Grbovic]]\n*''[[Wetlands (2011 film)|Wetlands]] (Mar\u00e9cages)'' by [[Guy \u00c9doin]]\n\n===Short Cuts Canada===\n[[File:Lightbox 2010-09-11 IV.JPG|thumb|The [[TIFF Bell Lightbox]] had its formal opening on September 12, 2010, during the 2010 festival. This shot was taken the day before the opening.]]\n*''[[4am (film)|4am]]'' by [[Janine Fung]]\n*''[[Acqua (film)|Acqua]]'' by [[Raha Shirazi]]\n*''[[Afternoon Tea]]'' by [[DJ Parmar]]\n*''[[Combustion (short film)|Combustion]]'' by [[Renaud Hall\u00e9e]]\n*''[[Derailments (short film)|Derailments]]'' by [[Chelsea McMullan]]\n*''[[The Devil's Due]]'' by [[Alexander Gorelick]]\n*''[[Doubles with Slight Pepper]]'' by [[Ian Harnarine]]\n*''[[The Encounter (short film)|The Encounter]]'' by [[Nicholas Pye]]\n*''[[A Film Portrait on Reconstructing 12 Possibilities that Preceded the Disappearance of Zoe Dean Drum]]'' by [[Eduardo Menz]]\n*''[[The Fuse: Or How I Burned Simon Bolivar]]'' by [[Igor Drlja\u010da]]\n*''[[Heart of Rhyme]]'' by [[Cory Bowles]]\n*''[[Hope (2011 film)|Hope]]'' by [[Pedro Pires (director)|Pedro Pires]]\n*''[[If I Can Fly]]'' by [[Yoakim B\u00e9langer]]\n*''[[Issues (film)|Issues]]'' by [[Enrico Colantoni]] and [[Hugh Dillon]] \n*''[[Lie Down and Die]]'' by [[Kyle Sanderson]]\n*''[[Little Theatres: Homage to the Mineral of Cabbage]]'' by [[Stephanie Dudley]]\n*''[[Mandeep]]'' by [[Darrin Klimek]]\n*''[[No Words Came Down]]'' by [[Ryan Flowers]]\n*''[[Of Events]]'' by [[Mathieu Tremblay]]\n*''[[One Night with You (short film)|One Night with You]]'' by [[Jeanne Leblanc]]\n*''[[Ora (film)|Ora]]'' by [[Philippe Baylaucq]]\n*''[[The Paris Quintet in Practice Makes Perfect]]'' by [[Benjamin Schuetze]]\n*''[[Patch Town]]'' by [[Craig Goodwill]