 (2011 film)|Play]]'' by [[Ruben \u00d6stlund]]\n*''[[Porfirio (film)|Porfirio]]'' by [[Alejandro Landes]]\n*''[[Random(film)|Random]]'' by [[Debbie Tucker Green]]\n*''[[The River Used to Be a Man]]'' by [[Jan Zabeil]]\n*''[[Swirl (film)|Swirl]]'' by [[Helv\u00e9cio Marins Jr.]]\n*''[[This Side of Resurrection]]'' by [[Joaquim Sapinho]]\n\n===Wavelengths===\n* ''[[349 (for Sol LeWitt)]]'' by [[Chris Kennedy (Canadian director)|Chris Kennedy]]\n* ''[[99 Clerkenwell Road]]'' by [[Sophie Michael]]\n* ''[[Aberration of Light: Dark Chamber Disclosure]]'' by [[Sandra Gibson]], [[Luis Recoder]] and [[Olivia Block]]\n* ''[[American Colour]]'' by [[Joshua Bonnetta]]\n* ''[[Ars colonia]]'' by [[Raya Martin]]\n* ''[[Black Mirror at the National Gallery]]'' by [[Mark Lewis (artist)|Mark Lewis]]\n* ''[[Bouquets 11-20]]'' by [[Rose Lowder]]\n* ''[[Chevelle (short film)|Chevelle]]'' by [[Kevin Jerome Everson]]\n* ''[[Coorow-Latham Road]]'' by [[Blake Williams (director)|Blake Williams]]\n* ''[[Edwin Parker]]'' by [[Tacita Dean]]\n* ''[[Empire (short film)|Empire]]'' by [[Apichatpong Weerasethakul]]\n* ''[[Found Cuban Mounts]]'' by [[Adriana Salazar Arroyo]]\n* ''[[I Will Forget This Day]]'' by [[Alina Rudnitskaya]]\n* ''[[Loutra/Baths]]'' by [[Nick Collins (director)|Nick Collins]]\n* ''[[Optra Field VII-IX]]'' by [[T. Marie]]\n* ''[[A Preface to Red]]'' by [[Jonathan Schwartz (filmmaker)|Jonathan Schwartz]]\n* ''[[Resonance (short film)|Resonance]]'' by [[Karen Johannesen]]\n* ''[[The Return (2011 film)|The Return]]'' by [[Nathaniel Dorsky]]\n* ''[[Sack Barrow]]'' by [[Ben Rivers]]\n* ''[[Sailboat (short film)|Sailboat]]'' by [[Joyce Wieland]]\n* ''[[Sea Series#10]]'' by [[John Price (filmmaker)|John Price]]\n* ''[[Space is the Place (short film)|Space is the Place]]'' by [[Eriko Sonoda]]\n* ''[[Twenty Cigarettes]]'' by [[James Benning (film director)|James Benning]]\n* ''[[Untitled (short film)|Untitled]]'' by [[Ne\u00efl Beloufa]]\n* ''[[Young Pines]]'' by [[Ute Aurand]]\n\n===